        <br/>
        <p>Visionary data scientists. Accomplished industry veterans. Trusted advisors. Proven investors. Our company is led by a world-class team that believes in data's potential to change the world. Our company is proud to be backed by Intel Capital, Investor Growth Capital (IGC), QuestMark Partners, Goldman Sachs, TransLink Capital, and many more other strategic investors.</p>
        <p>Please click on a profile below to get to know our team better!</p>
