        <div class="col-md-8 profileRight">
          <h2>Adam Anderson</h2>
          <h4>CEO &amp; Founder</h4>
          <p>Adam started the company on the basic premise that customer service and success should be the primary goal. His passion and vision for the development of the product has led to the flourishing of BAM, and the sky seems to be the limit for him in every endeavor he undertakes. In his free time, Adam enjoys long walks on the beach with his wife, and playing sports with his kids.</p>
