      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="profile2" class="profileDiv" title="Brian Baek">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4"><img src="assets/head02.png" height="200" width="200"></div>
        <div class="col-md-8 profileRight">
          <h2>Brian Baek</h2>
          <h4>CFO &amp; Co-Founder</h4>
          <p>Two years after Brian received his MBA from Seoul National University, he met Adam at a local coffee shop when they were both order the same type of latte. Brian now acts as CFO and is in charge of the financial direction of the company, as well as interfacing daily with investors. Brian is an avid fan of any Boston-area sports teams, and enjoys going fishing on the weekends.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="profile3" class="profileDiv" title="Christina Cook">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4"><img src="assets/head03.png" height="200" width="200"></div>
