          <h2>Christina Cook</h2>
          <h4>Recruiter</h4>
          <p>Christina recently graduated from UCLA with a major in Communications. She is now head of recruiting at BAM, and enjoys sourcing the brightest talent from around the world to participate in a global cause. Aside from the local Starbucks, Christina can often be found on hiking trails, reading a good book on a rainy day, or pondering the metaphysical nature of the universe.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="profile4" class="profileDiv" title="Daniel Dinwiddie">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4"><img src="assets/head04.png" height="200" width="200"></div>
        <div class="col-md-8 profileRight">
          <h2>Daniel Dinwiddie</h2>
          <h4>Project Manager</h4>
          <p>Ask anyone who the friendlist person in the office is, and most would say Daniel! He serves as project manager for several of BAM's most critical projects, and much of BAM's recent success can be attributed to his efforts. A tireless people-person and go-getter, Daniel surprisingly enjoys spending time at home with his 3 cats.</p>
