          <h2>Eric Eikelmann</h2>
          <h4>Software Engineer</h4>
          <p>Passionate about technology from a young age, Eric was delighted to be able to work as a software engineer at BAM. Eric's unique talents, skillset, and algorithms have all contributed greatly towards the products that BAM can offer today. BAM lives with his wife, 2 kids, and 4 dogs, and they all enjoy watching the latest superhero movies together.</p>
